data.description: This home sits on 5 lots in Lake Livingston Estates. It has a newly remodeled, large, farmhouse kitchen! Custom black walnut butcher block island is 10' long! Kitchen has a deep farmhouse sink, wet bar with mini fridge and TV all overlooking the family room. Home is tucked away in a quiet neighborhood with access to two boat ramps. There is an extra building on this property which once was the original home. It is perfect for storing all your outdoor accessories or turning it into a she shed or mancave! Great starter home for a anyone who wants space between them and their neighbors. Close to Lake Livingston and only miles from the town, this home is in the perfect spot!
